# Mycelium Phase 0 — provisioning .gitignore.
# Author: mindicator & silicon bags quartet
#
# Keeps deploy-time material out of version control. NONE of the *.example / *.j2 / role files are
# secrets; the files below are the real, per-deploy artefacts that an operator creates or that the
# playbook fetches back, and they MUST NOT be committed.

# Real inventory (copied from inventory.ini.example) — contains the node's reachability address.
inventory.ini

# Real group variables (copied from group_vars/all.yml.example) — contains donor selection,
# node_address, pinned checksums. Keep the .example tracked, ignore the real file.
group_vars/all.yml

# Operator output fetched from the node: rendered client subscriptions (contain client UUIDs in
# standard VLESS URIs) and the REALITY public key. Treat as sensitive; never commit.
out/

# Defensive: any local-only state, secrets, or sentinel-bearing files that may land here.
state/
secrets/
server.json
# Rendered AmneziaWG interface config (real keys) — only the .template is tracked.
awg0.conf
*.local
*.retry
